{"_id":"nhsdeathguard001","name":"Deathguard's Veil","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp","system":{"slug":"deathguards-veil","description":{"value":"<p>You are sharing a space with a Deathguard necrologist's horde. The press of twisted limbs and swirling ectoplasm hides you from view, making you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} to all creatures.</p><p><em>Applied automatically by the Necrologist Horde Sync module when an ally shares the horde's space. Removed automatically when the ally leaves.</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"GrantItem","uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W","onDeleteActions":{"granter":"restrict"}}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
{"_id":"nhsspirithorde01","name":"Spirit Horde","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-horde","description":{"value":"<p>This horde is composed of spirits rather than zombies. While active, the horde gains the incorporeal trait, immunity to disease, poison, and precision damage, and its Mobbing Assault deals void damage.</p><p><em>Granted automatically by Necrologist Horde Sync when the summoner has the Ghost Song feat and toggles Spirit Horde on. Removed when toggled off.</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"ActorTraits","add":["incorporeal"]},{"key":"Immunity","type":["disease","poison","precision"]},{"key":"DamageAlteration","mode":"override","property":"damage-type","value":"void","predicate":[{"or":["item:slug:mobbing-assault","item:name:Mobbing Assault"]}],"selectors":["mobbing-assault"]}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
{"_id":"nhsspirithordet1","name":"Spirit Horde Toggle","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/death/bones-crossed-orange.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-horde-toggle","description":{"value":"<p>Toggle this on when you Raise your Horde to make it a spirit horde (incorporeal, immunity to disease, poison, and precision, and Mobbing Assault deals void damage).</p><p><em>Automatic. Granted by Necrologist Horde Sync when you take the Ghost Song feat. Toggling this grants or removes the Spirit Horde effect on your linked horde(s).</em></p>"},"publication":{"title":"","authors":"","license":"OGL","remaster":false},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"category":"classfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":null,"rules":[{"key":"RollOption","option":"spirit-horde","toggleable":true,"value":false}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
